#                                     .epio links if no filename given
#       @(#)alstagein   6.6  17/4/96  -l xl introduced,  
#                                     multifiles not only for DLT's,
#                  10 files at a time for -q 1,11,21,31,41,51,61,71,81,91,
#                                     stageqry with -q , -s only once
